00:28:35,040 --> 00:28:41,200
think they've done a really good job of evolving 
those ideas overnight through the conversations  

315
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:45,920
they have and over dinner and walking, but 
then bringing that back the next day and being  

316
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:52,640
transparent about that and that's super important. 
If you are working in that kind of dynamic. There  

317
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:58,040
are definitely moments where I have missed 
out on a memo and stuff has rapidly proceeded,  

318
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:03,720
and I think I've just gotten used to that and 
gotten used to catching up really quickly,  

