321
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:19,640
There's moments where there's small alignments, 
there's more tectonic stuff that happens over  

322
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:25,560
months or years, and you need to realign at 
some stage. I think it happens with friendships,  

323
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:31,480
it happens with my wife, it happens with our 
product teams. There's always these moments  

324
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:50,484
where you need to re-communicate things and relay 
the land of it. And I think we've been great at  

